ical contributions, but you don&#8217;t have to code to contribute. Here are some of the ways you can make an impact without writing a single line of code:'=>'Efallai bod WordPress yn ffynnu ar gyfraniadau technegol, ond nid oes rhaid i chi allu codio i gyfrannu. Dyma rai o\'r ffyrdd y gallwch chi gael effaith heb ysgrifennu\'r un llinell o god:','No-code contribution'=>'Cyfrannu heb godio','Grow your network and make friends.'=>'Tyfu eich rhwydwaith a gwneud ffrindiau.','Apply your skills or learn new ones.'=>'Cyfrannu eich sgiliau neu ddysgu rhai newydd.','Be part of a global open source community.'=>'Bod yn rhan o gymuned cod agored fyd-eang.','Join the diverse WordPress contributor community and connect with other people who are passionate about maintaining a free and open web.'=>'Ymunwch â chymuned cyfranwyr WordPress a chysylltwch ag eraill sy\'n angerddol am gynnal gwe agored, rhad ac am ddim.','Do you use WordPress for work, for personal projects, or even just for fun? You can help shape the long-term success of the open source project that powers millions of websites around the world.'=>'Ydych chi\'n defnyddio WordPress ar gyfer gwaith, ar gyfer projectau personol, neu hyd yn oed dim ond am hwyl? Gallwch chi helpu i lunio llwyddiant hirdymor y prosiect cod agored sy\'n pweru miliynau o wefannau ledled y byd.','Be the future of WordPress'=>'Byddwch yn ddyfodol WordPress','<a href="%1$s">Learn WordPress</a> is a free resource for new and experienced WordPress users. Learn is stocked with how-to videos on using various features in WordPress, <a href="%2$s">interactive workshops</a> for exploring topics in-depth, and lesson plans for diving deep into specific areas of WordPress.'=>'Mae <a href="%1$s">Learn WordPress</a> yn adnodd rhad ac am ddim i ddefnyddwyr WordPress newydd a phrofiadol. Mae gan Learn stoc o fideos sut i ddefnyddio amrywiol nodweddion WordPress, <a href="%2$s">digwyddiadau rhyngweithiol</a> ar gyfer archwilio pynciau yn fanwl, a chynlluniau gwersi ar gyfer plymio\'n ddwfn i feysydd penodol WordPress.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forums/">Support forums</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forums/">Fforymau cymorth</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-widgets-screen-classic-editor/">Documentation on Widgets</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-widgets-screen-classic-editor/">Dogfennaeth Teclynnau</a>','<strong>View</strong> takes you to a public author archive which lists all the posts published by the user.'=>'Mae <strong>Golwg</strong> yn mynd â chi i archif awdur cyhoeddus sy\'n rhestru\'r holl gofnodion a gyhoeddwyd gan y defnyddiwr.','<strong>Download file</strong> downloads the original media file to your device.'=>'<strong>Llwytho ffeil i lawr</strong> yn llwytho i lawr y ffeil cyfryngau gwreiddiol i\'ch dyfais.','site editor title tagEditor'=>'Golygydd','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">Documentation on Auto-updates</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">Dogfennaeth ar Awto-ddiweddariadau</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customize-date-and-time-format/">Documentation on date and time formatting</a>.'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customize-date-and-time-format/">Dogfennaeth ar fformatio dyddiad ac amser</a> .','You can set the language, and WordPress will automatically download and install the translation files (available if your filesystem is writable).'=>'Gallwch chi osod yr iaith, a bydd WordPress yn llwytho i lawr ac yn gosod y ffeiliau cyfieithu\'n awtomatig (ar gael os yw\'ch system ffeiliau yn ysgrifenadwy).','If you want site visitors to be able to register themselves, check the membership box. If you want the site administrator to register every new user, leave the box unchecked. In either case, you can set a default user role for all new users.'=>'Os ydych am i ymwelwyr i\'ch gwefan allu cofrestru eu hunain, ticiwch y blwch aelodaeth. Os ydych chi am i weinyddwr y wefan gofrestru pob defnyddiwr newydd, gadewch y blwch heb ei dicio. Yn y naill achos neu\'r llall, gallwch chi osod rôl defnyddiwr rhagosodedig ar gyfer pob defnyddiwr newydd.','Both WordPress URL and site URL can start with either %1$s or %2$s. A URL starting with %2$s requires an SSL certificate, so be sure that you have one before changing to %2$s. With %2$s, a padlock will appear next to the address in the browser address bar. Both %2$s and the padlock signal that your site meets some basic security requirements, which can build trust with your visitors and with search engines.'=>'Gall URL WordPress ac URL gwefan ddechrau gyda naill ai %1$s neu %2$s. Mae URL sy\'n dechrau gyda %2$s angen tystysgrif SSL, felly gwnewch yn siŵr bod gennych un cyn newid i %2$s. Gyda %2$s, bydd clo clap yn ymddangos wrth ymyl y cyfeiriad ym mar cyfeiriad y porwr. Mae %2$s a\'r clo clap yn dangos bod eich gwefan yn bodloni rhai gofynion diogelwch sylfaenol, a all feithrin ymddiriedaeth gyda\'ch ymwelwyr a pheiriannau chwilio.','Though the terms refer to two different concepts, in practice, they can be the same address or different. For example, you can have the core WordPress installation files in the root directory (<code>https://example.com</code>), in which case the two URLs would be the same. Or the <a href="%s">WordPress files can be in a subdirectory</a> (<code>https://example.com/wordpress</code>). In that case, the WordPress URL and the site URL would be different.'=>'Er bod y termau\'n cyfeirio at ddau gysyniad gwahanol, yn ymarferol, maen nhw\'n gallu bod yr un cyfeiriad neu\'n rhai gwahanol. Er enghraifft, gallwch gael y ffeiliau gosod WordPress craidd yn y cyfeiriadur gwraidd ( <code>https://example.com</code> ), ac os felly byddai\'r ddau URL yr un peth. Neu <a href="%s">gall y ffeiliau WordPress fod mewn is-gyfeiriadur</a> ( <code>https://example.com/wordpress</code> ). Yn yr achos hwnnw, bydd URL WordPress ac URL y wefan yn wahanol.','Two terms you will want to know are the WordPress URL and the site URL. The WordPress URL is where the core WordPress installation files are, and the site URL is the address a visitor uses in the browser to go to your site.'=>'Dau derm y byddwch am eu gwybod yw URL WordPress ac URL y wefan. URL WordPress yw lle mae\'r ffeiliau gosod WordPress craidd, ac URL y wefan yw\'r cyfeiriad y mae ymwelydd yn ei ddefnyddio yn y porwr i fynd i\'ch gwefan.','RoboHash (Generated)'=>'RoboHash (Cynhyrchwyd)','site editor menu itemEditor'=>'Golygydd','Allow <a href="%s">trackbacks and pingbacks</a>'=>'Caniatáu <a href="%s">hysbysiadau cydnabod a hysbysiadau cyfeirio</a>','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/assign-custom-fields/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/assign-custom-fields/','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/what-is-an-excerpt-classic-editor/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/what-is-an-excerpt-classic-editor/','%s expects a non-empty string.'=>'Mae %s yn disgwyl llinyn nad yw\'n wag.','The destination directory already exists and could not be removed.'=>'Mae\'r cyfeiriadur cyrchfan eisoes yn bodoli ac nid oedd modd ei ddileu.','The destination folder already exists.'=>'Mae\'r ffolder cyrchfan eisoes yn bodoli.','The source and destination are the same.'=>'Mae\'r ffynhonnell a\'r gyrchfan yr un peth.','Expand or collapse the elements by clicking on their headings, and arrange them by dragging their headings or by clicking on the up and down arrows.'=>'Ehangwch neu gwympwch yr elfennau trwy glicio ar eu penawdau, a threfnwch nhw trwy lusgo eu penawdau neu drwy glicio ar y saethau i fyny ac i lawr.','Download &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'Llwytho “%s” i lawr','The "%s" argument must be a non-empty string.'=>'Rhaid i\'r ymresymiad "%s" fod yn llinyn nad yw\'n wag.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/write-posts-classic-editor/">Documentation on Writing and Editing Posts</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/write-posts-classic-editor/">Dogfennaeth ar Ysgrifennu a Golygu Cofnodion</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/keyboard-shortcuts-classic-editor/#keyboard-shortcuts-for-comments">Documentation on Keyboard Shortcuts</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/keyboard-shortcuts-classic-editor/#keyboard-shortcuts-for-comments">Dogfennaeth ar Lwybrau Byr Bysellfwrdd</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/understand-comment-spam/">Documentation on Comment Spam</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/understand-comment-spam/">Dogfennaeth ar Sbam Sylwadau</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/">Documentation on Customizer</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/">Dogfennaeth ar y Cyfaddaswr</a>','https://wordpress.org/download/'=>'https://wordpress.org/download/','This is the final release of WordPress %s'=>'Dyma fersiwn olaf WordPress %s','Site Editor'=>'Golygydd Gwefan','<strong>Send password reset</strong> sends the user an email with a link to set a new password.'=>'Mae <strong>anfon ailosod cyfrinair</strong> yn anfon e-bost at y defnyddiwr gyda dolen i osod cyfrinair newydd.','https://developer.wordpress.org/apis/wp-config-php/#wp-environment-type'=>'https://developer.wordpress.org/apis/wp-config-php/#wp-environment-type','<strong>Copy URL</strong> copies the URL for the media file to your clipboard.'=>'Mae <strong>Copïwch URL</strong> yn copïo\'r URL ar gyfer y ffeil cyfryngau i\'ch clipfwrdd.','<strong>View</strong> will take you to a public display page for that file.'=>'Mae <strong>Gweld</strong> yn mynd â chi i dudalen arddangos gyhoeddus ar gyfer y ffeil honno.','<strong>Delete Permanently</strong> will delete the file from the media library (as well as from any posts to which it is currently attached).'=>'Bydd <strong>Dileu\'n Barhaol</strong> yn dileu\'r ffeil o lyfrgell y cyfryngau (yn ogystal ag o unrhyw gofnodion y mae wedi\'u hatodi iddynt ar hyn o bryd).','<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to a simple screen to edit that individual file&#8217;s metadata. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the media file name or thumbnail.'=>'Mae <strong>Golygu</strong> yn mynd â chi i sgrin syml i olygu metadata&#39;r ffeil unigol honno. Gallwch hefyd gyrraedd y sgrin honno trwy glicio ar enw&#39;r ffeil cyfryngau neu&#39;r llun bach.','Hovering over a row reveals action links that allow you to manage media items. You can perform the following actions:'=>'Mae hofran dros res yn datgelu dolenni gweithredu sy\'n eich galluogi i reoli eitemau cyfryngau. Gallwch gyflawni\'r gweithredoedd canlynol:','themesBlock Themes'=>'Themâu Bloc','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/">Documentation on Block Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/">Dogfennaeth ar Themâu Bloc</a>','Block themes'=>'Themâu bloc','With a block theme, you can place and edit blocks without affecting your content by customizing or creating new templates.'=>'Gyda thema bloc, gallwch osod a golygu blociau heb effeithio ar eich cynnwys trwy gyfaddasu neu greu templedi newydd.','A block theme is a theme that uses blocks for all parts of a site including navigation menus, header, content, and site footer. These themes are built for the features that allow you to edit and customize all parts of your site.'=>'Thema bloc yw thema sy\'n defnyddio blociau ar gyfer pob rhan o wefan gan gynnwys dewislenni llywio, pennyn, cynnwys a throedyn gwefan. Mae\'r themâu hyn wedi\'u hadeiladu ar gyfer y nodweddion sy\'n eich galluogi i olygu a chyfaddasu pob rhan o\'ch gwefan.','Recommended items are considered beneficial to your site, although not as important to prioritize as a critical issue. They may include improvements in areas such as security, performance, and user experience.'=>'Ystyriwn fod eitemau sy\'n cael eu hargymhelli yn fuddiol i\'ch gwefan, er nad ydyn nhw mor bwysig i\'w blaenoriaethu â mater critigol. Gallan nhw gynnwys gwelliannau mewn meysydd fel diogelwch, perfformiad a phrofiad y defnyddiwr.','Critical issues are items that may have a high impact on your site&#8217;s performance or security. Resolving these issues should be prioritized.'=>'Mae materion critigol yn eitemau sy\'n gallu cael effaith fawr ar berfformiad neu ddiogelwch eich gwefan. Rhaid blaenoriaethu datrys y problemau hyn.','Configuration rules for %s:'=>'Rheolau ffurfweddu ar gyfer %s:','Customize permalink structure by selecting available tags'=>'Cyfaddasu strwythur cyswllt parhaol trwy ddewis y tagiau sydd ar gael','Select the permalink structure for your website. Including the %s tag makes links easy to understand, and can help your posts rank higher in search engines.'=>'Dewiswch y strwythur cyswllt parhaol ar gyfer eich gwefan. Mae cynnwys y tag %s yn gwneud dolenni\'n hawdd i\'w deall, a gall helpu eich cofnodion i raddio\'n uwch mewn peiriannau chwilio.','%s removed from permalink structure'=>'%s wedi\'i dynnu o strwythur cyswllt parhaol','Site Health %s'=>'Iechyd Gwefan %s','Theme Styles & Block Settings'=>'Arddulliau Thema a Gosodiadau Bloc','The minimum recommended version of PHP is %s.'=>'Y fersiwn lleiaf a argymhellir o PHP yw %s.','PHP is one of the programming languages used to build WordPress. Newer versions of PHP receive regular security updates and may increase your site&#8217;s performance.'=>'PHP yw un o\'r ieithoedd rhaglennu sy\'n cael ei ddefnyddio i adeiladu WordPress. Mae fersiynau mwy newydd o PHP yn derbyn diweddariadau diogelwch rheolaidd a gallant gynyddu perfformiad eich gwefan.','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which soon will not be supported by WordPress. Ensure that PHP is updated on your server as soon as possible. Otherwise you will not be able to upgrade WordPress.'=>'Mae eich gwefan yn rhedeg ar hen fersiwn o PHP (%s), na fydd yn cael ei gefnogi gan WordPress yn fuan. Sicrhewch fod PHP yn cael ei ddiweddaru ar eich gweinydd cyn gynted â phosibl. Fel arall, ni fyddwch yn gallu uwchraddio WordPress.','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which does not receive security updates and soon will not be supported by WordPress. Ensure that PHP is updated on your server as soon as possible. Otherwise you will not be able to upgrade WordPress.'=>'Mae eich gwefan yn rhedeg ar hen fersiwn o PHP (%s), nad yw\'n derbyn diweddariadau diogelwch ac ni fydd yn cael ei chefnogi gan WordPress yn fuan. Sicrhewch fod PHP yn cael ei ddiweddaru ar eich gweinydd cyn gynted â phosibl. Fel arall, ni fyddwch yn gallu uwchraddio WordPress.','Persistent object cache'=>'Storfan gwrthrych parhaus','Page cache'=>'Storfan tudalen','You should use a persistent object cache'=>'Dylech ddefnyddio storfan gwrthrych parhaus','Your host appears to support the following object caching services: %s.'=>'Mae\'n ymddangos bod eich gwesteiwr yn cefnogi\'r gwasanaethau storio gwrthrych canlynol: %s.','Your hosting provider can tell you if a persistent object cache can be enabled on your site.'=>'Gall eich darparwr gwesteio ddweud wrthych a oes modd galluogi storfan gwrthrychau parhaus ar eich gwefan.','A persistent object cache is not required'=>'Nid oes angen storfan gwrthrychau parhaus','Learn more about persistent object caching.'=>'Dysgwch fwy am storio gwrthrychau parhaus.','A persistent object cache makes your site&#8217;s database more efficient, resulting in faster load times because WordPress can retrieve your site&#8217;s content and settings much more quickly.'=>'Mae storfan gwrthrychau parhaus yn gwneud cronfa ddata eich gwefan yn fwy effeithlon, gan arwain at amseroedd llwytho cyflymach oherwydd gall WordPress adfer cynnwys a gosodiadau eich gwefan yn gynt o lawer.','A persistent object cache is being used'=>'Mae storfan gwrthrychau parhaus yn cael ei ddefnyddio','A page cache plugin was not detected.'=>'Heb ganfod ategyn storfan tudalen.','A page cache plugin was detected.'=>'Canfuwyd ategyn storfan tudalen.','There was %d client caching response header detected:'=>'Canfuwyd %d pennyn ymateb storfan cleient:' . "\0" . 'Canfuwyd %d pennyn ymateb storfan cleient:' . "\0" . 'Canfuwyd %d pennyn ymateb storfan cleient:' . "\0" . 'Canfuwyd %d pennyn ymateb storfan cleient:','No client caching response headers were detected.'=>'Heb ganfod unrhyw benynnau ymateb storfan caching cleient.','Median server response time was %1$s milliseconds. It should be less than the recommended %2$s milliseconds threshold.'=>'Yr amser ymateb gweinydd canolrifol oedd %1$s milieiliad. Dylai fod yn llai na\'r trothwy %2$s milieiliadau sy\'n cael eu hargymell.','Median server response time was %1$s milliseconds. This is less than the recommended %2$s milliseconds threshold.'=>'Yr amser ymateb gweinydd canolrifol oedd %1$s milieiliad. Dylai fod yn llai na\'r trothwy %2$s milieiliadau sy\'n cael eu hargymell.','Server response time could not be determined. Verify that loopback requests are working.'=>'Nid oedd modd pennu amser ymateb y gweinydd. Gwiriwch fod ceisiadau cylch ôl yn gweithio.','Page cache is detected but the server response time is still slow'=>'Canfuwyd storfan tudalen ond mae amser ymateb y gweinydd yn araf o hyd','Page cache is not detected and the server response time is slow'=>'Heb ganfod storfan tudalen ac mae amser ymateb y gweinydd yn araf','Page cache is detected and the server response time is good'=>'Canfuwyd storfan tudalen ac mae amser ymateb y gweinydd yn dda','Page cache is not detected but the server response time is OK'=>'Heb ganfod storfan tudalen ac mae amser ymateb y gweinydd yn iawn','Unable to detect page cache due to possible loopback request problem. Please verify that the loopback request test is passing. Error: %1$s (Code: %2$s)'=>'Methu canfod storfan tudalen oherwydd problem cais cylch ôl posib. Gwiriwch fod y prawf cais cylch ôl yn llwyddiannus. Gwall: %1$s (Cod: %2$s)','Unable to detect the presence of page cache'=>'Methu canfod presenoldeb storfan tudalennau','Learn more about page cache'=>'Dysgu rhagor am storfan tudalen','Page cache is detected by looking for an active page cache plugin as well as making three requests to the homepage and looking for one or more of the following HTTP client caching response headers:'=>'Mae storfan tudalen yn cael ei ganfod trwy chwilio am ategyn storfan tudalen gweithredol yn ogystal â gwneud tri chais i\'r hafan a chwilio am un neu fwy o\'r penawdau ymateb storfan y cleient HTTP canlynol:','Page cache enhances the speed and performance of your site by saving and serving static pages instead of calling for a page every time a user visits.'=>'Mae storfan tudalen yn gwella cyflymder a pherfformiad eich gwefan trwy chadw a gweini tudalennau sefydlog yn lle galw am dudalen bob tro y bydd defnyddiwr yn ymweld.','If you are still seeing this warning after having tried the actions below, you may need to contact your hosting provider for further assistance.'=>'Os ydych chi\'n dal i weld y rhybudd hwn ar ôl rhoi cynnig ar y camau isod, efallai y bydd angen i chi gysylltu â\'ch darparwr cynnal am ragor o gymorth.','The Authorization header is used by third-party applications you have approved for this site. Without this header, those apps cannot connect to your site.'=>'Mae\'r pennyn Awdurdodi yn cael ei ddefnyddio gan raglenni trydydd parti rydych chi wedi\'u cymeradwyo ar gyfer y wefan hon. Heb y pennyn hwn, ni all yr apiau hynny gysylltu â\'ch gwefan.','When testing the REST API, an unexpected result was returned:'=>'Wrth brofi\'r API REST, dychwelwyd canlyniad annisgwyl:','REST API Response: (%1$s) %2$s'=>'Ymateb REST API: (%1$s) %2$s','REST API Endpoint: %s'=>'Diweddbwynt REST API: %s','When testing the REST API, an error was encountered:'=>'Wrth brofi\'r API REST, cafwyd gwall:','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which does not