s oes diweddariad ar gael, bydd hysbysiad yn ymddangos yn y Bar Offer a\'r ddewislen llywio.','<strong>Themes and Plugins</strong> &mdash; To update individual themes or plugins from this screen, use the checkboxes to make your selection, then <strong>click on the appropriate &#8220;Update&#8221; button</strong>. To update all of your themes or plugins at once, you can check the box at the top of the section to select all before clicking the update button.'=>'<strong>Themâu ac Ategion</strong> &mdash; Er mwyn diweddaru themâu unigol neu ategion o\'r sgrin hon, dewiswch drwy ddefnyddio\'r blychau ticio, yna <strong>cliciwch ar y botwm &#8220;Diweddaru&#8221; priodol</strong>. Er mwyn diweddaru eich holl themâu ac ategion ar un waith, mae modd i chi dicio\'r blwch ar frig y dewis i ddewis y cyfan cyn clicio\'r botwm diweddaru.','On this screen, you can update to the latest version of WordPress, as well as update your themes, plugins, and translations from the WordPress.org repositories.'=>'Ar y sgrin hon, gallwch ddiweddaru i fersiwn ddiweddaraf WordPress, yn ogystal â diweddaru eich themâu a\'ch ategion a chyfieithiadau o storfeydd WordPress.org.','If you would like to see more themes to choose from, click on the &#8220;Add Theme&#8221; button and you will be able to browse or search for additional themes from the <a href="%s">WordPress Theme Directory</a>. Themes in the WordPress Theme Directory are designed and developed by third parties, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses. Oh, and they are free!'=>'Os hoffech weld mwy o themâu i ddewis ohonyn nhw, cliciwch ar y botwm &quot;Ychwanegu Thema&quot; a byddwch yn gallu pori neu chwilio am themâu ychwanegol o&#39;r <a href="%s">Cyfeiriadur Thema WordPress</a> . Mae themâu yn y Cyfeiriadur Themâu WordPress yn cael eu dylunio a&#39;u datblygu gan drydydd partïon, ac maen nhwn\'n gydnaws â&#39;r drwydded y mae WordPress yn ei defnyddio. O, ac maen nhw&#39;n rhad ac am ddim!','%1$s MB (%2$s%%) Space Used'=>'%